{
  "stem": "18056.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 77.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Poland, in the city where I lived, there were something like 8,000 people, of which there were about 1,000 or 1,200 Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very large Jewish population, because there was a lot of textile going on in that area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the textile business, there were a lot of Jewish people involved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think because of that maybe, there was a larger Jewish population than normally in some other cities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in Poland, there were about 3 and 1/2 million Jews, large population of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was on the-- we only had about three or four Jewish children in my class.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, when class was over, school was over, I had to make sure to get home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know-- and a lot of the kids there, they-- they were waiting for that to beat me up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Being that I was strong and husky and was very fast and running, I was able to negotiate out a pretty good deal for myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was really never really beaten up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- but I did beat up a few others who wanted to beat me up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this is from that point of view, as a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, the anti-Semitism was more-- was more important for the-- for the grown-ups.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They could do something about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we talked not only with my parents, but also with the people that lived in that city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You must understand there were at least about 10% or 15% of the population of Konstantynow were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
